text: Bagshot Park (Grid reference: ) is a royal residence. It is south of Windsor. It is located in Bagshot, Surrey, and is the current home and official residence of Prince Edward, the Earl of Wessex and Sophie, Countess of Wessex. Bagshot Park is a few miles from Sunninghill Park, the former home of Prince Andrew, Duke of York. Category:Royal residences in the United Kingdom
title: Bagshot Park
